Added support for OSC 1.0 array type tags '[' (LO_ARRAY_BEGIN) and ']' (LO_ARRAY_END). These are zero-data type tags that follow the same pattern as LO_TRUE, LO_FALSE, LO_NIL, and LO_INFINITUM throughout the codebase. Changes span the type enum, message serialization/deserialization, pretty-printing, endian handling, the C++ wrapper, and the oscsend CLI tool.
